summary: Completed comprehensive frontend testing of SaaSy Cookies product studio website. All features working perfectly - homepage sections, navigation, SEO pages, functional tools (Invoice Generator with live preview and QR Code Generator), and mobile responsiveness.
passed_tests: Homepage hero section with correct title 'We build tools that matter.'
SenseAI and Pacific Market CTA buttons functional
What We Build section with 3 category cards (AI Products, Community Platforms, Developer Tools)
Featured Products section with working SenseAI and Pacific Market cards
Free Tools section with Invoice Generator and QR Code Generator cards
Coming Soon section with 'More tools on the way' messaging
Navigation bar with working logo and all nav links
Footer with functional Contact, Privacy, Terms links
SenseAI page with all sections (hero, problem, shift, use cases, founder POV, CTA)
Pacific Market page with all sections (hero, gap, vision, tech as enabler, founder story, CTA)
Invoice Generator fully functional: form fields, line items, add/remove items, tax calculations, live preview, Download PDF
QR Generator fully functional: text input updates QR code, size options, color presets, Download PNG and Copy buttons
Contact page with working contact form and all input fields
Privacy page loads with complete privacy policy content
Terms page loads with complete terms of service content
Mobile menu toggle works correctly on small screens
Mobile navigation links function properly and menu closes after selection
All navigation routes work without 404 errors
